{"id": "ozv1665702766897", "title": "examine", "breadcrumbs": ["Testing and Debugging", "Debugging Uniface Applications", "Debugging in Character Mode", "examine"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ozv1665702766897.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">examine</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   dump \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   dump \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/whw1665702766757.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:  filter  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:  filter  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mbf1665702767040.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/ozv1665702766897.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/ozv1665702766897.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/ozv1665702766897.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530823\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530823\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ozv1665702766897.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ozv1665702766897.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ozv1665702766897.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ozv1665702766897\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      examine\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__examine_66088\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Display the contents of a field, function, or variable, or change the contents of variables or selected ProcScript functions.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__topic_d19259e1_d19260e1_d19261e1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__1\">\n Object\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__2\">\n Sytax for Examine\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__3\">\n Syntax for Change\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__1\">\n Fields:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">.Entity</var> } </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__3\">\n Not applicable\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__1\">\n ProcScript functions:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Function</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>} <p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Function</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>}</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__3\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcFunction</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n<p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcFunction</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__1\">\n Component, global, and general variables:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__3\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n<p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__1\">\n General variables ($1-$99) only:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__3\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__1\">\n Local variables:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ozv1665702766897__table_d2132e1_d2133e1_d2134e1__entry__3\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Examine</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__topic_d13872e1_d13873e1_d13874e1_d13875e1_d13876e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d369723e279\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9449e1_d9450e1_d9451e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">.Entity</var>—display the field value; if <var class=\"keyword varname\">.Entity</var> is omitted, the current field is assumed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9452e1_d9453e1_d9454e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Function</var>—display the current value of the specified ProcScript function. Some functions cannot be examined.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9455e1_d9456e1_d9457e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var>—variable name or number. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9458e1_d9459e1_d9460e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcFunction</var>—one of\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>,\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$selblk</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9461e1_d9462e1_d9463e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>—set the function or\n               variable to this value. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__topic_d13877e1_d13878e1_d13879e1_d13880e1_d13881e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d369723e333\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__p_d19268e1_d19269e1_d19270e1\">The examine command enables you to see the current value of a field, function, or variable. When used with =Value it can be used to set the value variables and selected ProcScript functions. Except for fields and local variables, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">examine</code> keyword can often be omitted.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__topic_d13882e1_d13883e1_d13884e1_d13885e1_d13886e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d369723e345\">\n                        \n Examining and Setting Variables\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__p_d19274e1_d19275e1_d19276e1\">Specifying a <var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var> without <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var> displays the current value of the variable.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__p_d19277e1_d19278e1_d19279e1\">When <code class=\"ph codeph\">examine</code> is used in the command, general variables can be referenced by number, without the leading dollar sign ($). When no arguments are specified, <code class=\"ph codeph\">examine</code> displays the contents of the next sequentially numbered general variable.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__p_d19280e1_d19281e1_d19282e1\">Within the debugger, the ProcScript functions <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$selblk</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> can also be referred to as <code class=\"ph codeph\">$100</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">$101</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">$102</code>, and <code class=\"ph codeph\">$103</code> respectively.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__topic_d13887e1_d13888e1_d13889e1_d13890e1_d13891e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d369723e401\">\n                        \n Excluded Functions\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__p_d19286e1_d19287e1_d19288e1\">Functions that cannot be examined in the character mode debugger include:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9464e1_d9465e1_d9466e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$logical</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9467e1_d9468e1_d9469e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$text</code>—the value of a specific message can be examined using the debugger <code class=\"ph codeph\">message</code> command.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9470e1_d9471e1_d9472e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$textexist</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9473e1_d9474e1_d9475e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$web</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9476e1_d9477e1_d9478e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$subsetreturn</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9479e1_d9480e1_d9481e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$fielddbvalue</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9482e1_d9483e1_d9484e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$clock</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9485e1_d9486e1_d9487e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$condition</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9488e1_d9489e1_d9490e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$expression</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9491e1_d9492e1_d9493e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$date</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9494e1_d9495e1_d9496e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$datim</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9497e1_d9498e1_d9499e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$number</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9500e1_d9501e1_d9502e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$syntax</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__li_d9503e1_d9504e1_d9505e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$time</code>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__section_cft_fjb_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d369723e502\">Example: Examining Data</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Display the value of the field NAME.HORSE:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_zv2_kjb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">e name.horse</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Display the name of the current entity:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_aw2_kjb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ex $entname</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Display the field modification status of the field NAME.HORSE:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_bw2_kjb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldmod(name.horse)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Display the value of the component variable $TEMP$:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_cw2_kjb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$temp$</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Display the value of the local variable <code class=\"ph codeph\">myvar1</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_dw2_kjb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">e myvar1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Display the value of general variables $79 and $81:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_ew2_kjb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">e 79\n$81</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__section_mdn_y3b_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d369723e552\">Example: Changing Values of Variables and ProcScript Functions</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set the value of the component variable $TEMP$:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_sxw_y3b_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$temp$=0</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Set the value of global variable $$CITY:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_txw_y3b_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$$city=Amsterdam</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Set the value of general variable $47:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_uxw_y3b_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ex 47 = 14.2</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Set the value of local variable TOTAL:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_vxw_y3b_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">e total = 0</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Set the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozv1665702766897__pre_wxw_y3b_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">4100 = -1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cvk1665702766970.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>message</a><p>Display the text of a message.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530823\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530823\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "examine Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 examine Display the contents of a field, function, or variable, or change the contents of variables or selected ProcScript functions. Object Sytax for Examine Syntax for Change Fields: Examine Field { .Entity } Not applicable ProcScript functions: Examine Function { ( Name ) } Function { ( Name ) } Examine ProcFunction = Value ProcFunction = Value Component, global, and general variables: Examine Variable Variable Examine Variable = Value Variable = Value General variables ($1-$99) only: Examine Number Examine Examine Number = Value Local variables: Examine Variable Examine Number = Value Arguments Field .Entity —display the field value; if .Entity is omitted, the current field is assumed. Function —display the current value of the specified ProcScript function. Some functions cannot be examined. Variable —variable name or number. ProcFunction —one of $status , $result , $selblk , or $format . Value —set the function or variable to this value. Description The examine command enables you to see the current value of a field, function, or variable. When used with =Value it can be used to set the value variables and selected ProcScript functions. Except for fields and local variables, the examine keyword can often be omitted. Examining and Setting Variables Specifying a Variable without = Value displays the current value of the variable. When examine is used in the command, general variables can be referenced by number, without the leading dollar sign ($). When no arguments are specified, examine displays the contents of the next sequentially numbered general variable. Within the debugger, the ProcScript functions $status , $result , $selblk , and $format can also be referred to as $100 , $101 , $102 , and $103 respectively. Excluded Functions Functions that cannot be examined in the character mode debugger include: $logical $text —the value of a specific message can be examined using the debugger message command. $textexist $web $subsetreturn $fielddbvalue $clock $condition $expression $date $datim $number $syntax $time Example: Examining Data Display the value of the field NAME.HORSE: e name.horse Copy Display the name of the current entity: ex $entname Copy Display the field modification status of the field NAME.HORSE: $fieldmod(name.horse) Copy Display the value of the component variable $TEMP$: $temp$ Copy Display the value of the local variable myvar1 : e myvar1 Copy Display the value of general variables $79 and $81: e 79 $81 Copy Example: Changing Values of Variables and ProcScript Functions Set the value of the component variable $TEMP$: $temp$=0 Copy Set the value of global variable $$CITY: $$city=Amsterdam Copy Set the value of general variable $47: ex 47 = 14.2 Copy Set the value of local variable TOTAL: e total = 0 Copy Set the value of $status : 4100 = -1 Copy Related Links message Display the text of a message. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}